web_research.query: What is the bbox3 algorithm in Santa 2025 Kaggle competition?
web_research.finding: bbox3 is a specialized packing algorithm / tool created to compute the bounding‑box solution for the Christmas‑tree packing problem in the Santa 2025 Kaggle competition, as discussed in the competition’s forum on Jan 4 2026 ([kaggle.com](https://www.kaggle.com/competitions/santa-2025/discussion/665978)).
